      • onOadEvent

        void onOadEvent(OADEvent event,
                int value)
        Callback triggered when a new step of the OAD (Over the Air Download) has completed.
        Parameters:
        event - the event code associated with the step. See OADEvent for the list of events
        value - the value associated with the step. Might indicate a progress, a success or a failure
